title: Vote for the third round Golff Farm Mining（第3轮Golff Farm矿池投票）
body:
Any user who holds GOF can participate in the Golff Farm candidate voting since 2 AM, 09/29/2020 to  2 AM 09/30/2020(UTC).   Users vote for the top six tokens to participate in Golff Farm The 3rd round (2 weeks) of mining!

Golff第三轮流动性挖矿候选人投票已经正式开启，请所有持有GOF的社区用户为您所支持的候选项目进行投票。最终投票前六名的项目代币将入选参与Golff Farm第3轮（两周）的挖矿！用户可质押对应项目代币参与获得GOF挖矿奖励。
author: 0xEdba3A794B15880659b4459E02350C1c73cE2375
